        MoreKeys {
            bindings = <
&none  &none             &none              &none                 &none                  &none  &none     &none          &none      &none      &none  &none
&none  &kp LESS_THAN     &kp GREATER_THAN   &kp LEFT_BRACE        &kp RIGHT_BRACE        &none  &none     &none          &none      &none      &none  &none
